  errorButtonOnPress: () => void;
  hasError?: boolean;
  handleGoToHome?: () => void;
  currentRouteName?: string;
  handleClose?: () => void;
  scrollViewRef?: RefObject<ScrollView>;
}
```

### Key Features:
- Wraps content with a keyboard-avoiding container
- Renders StatusBar + optional Header with navigation icons
- Optional HeaderTitle section (alternative to standard header)
- Loading modal overlay ("Aguarde...")
- Error modal overlay with retry and home navigation buttons
- Optional ScrollView wrapper
- Right secondary icon toggle support
- Used by hook pattern: index.tsx (logic) + view.tsx (render)

